{
  "stem": "11671.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was directing traffic and telling which person should go on which side, which in essence was who will live and who will die, because we didn't know that but he was picking the able-bodied, nice looking to one side and then the frail-looking, the older person and very young to the other side.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were just standing there, and just everything was very fast, you know, just shouting and mobs and people crying and-- Well, next thing we know, we were out of that line, and we were marched to another location, which was-- we were both in C Lager  and B Lager.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So one of them was-- the first lager was, I think, C Lager, and we were in B Lager.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we ended up in C Lager, which one lager was where the crematorium ovens were and the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then people were selected from there and then they were sent to the other camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't find out for the longest time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we were marched to a barracks, and then we were told to undress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first person went to one room, and the person first cut our hair off, first with the scissor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went to the next room, and then they shaved us all, both our hair and under the arm and the pubic hair, everyplace.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were told that for sanitary reasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my sister was standing next to me and was yelling my name, Pszi, where are you?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and I was right next to her, and did not-- she did not recognize me, because I, I was-- I had waist-length hair, and here I was shaven.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So from there, you know, we went to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
